# Predefined Callback Structures

**API Collection**

`CFBinaryHeap` provides some predefined callbacks for your convenience.

## Constants

- **kCFStringBinaryHeapCallBacks**: Predefined [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFBinaryHeapCallBacks] structure containing a set of callbacks appropriate for use when the values in a binary heap are all `CFString` objects.
